\mathcal{L}[\sin at] = \frac{a}{s^2 + a^2}
\frac{d}{dt}(\sin at) = a\cos at
\int \sin at \, dt = -\frac{1}{a}\cos at

\mathcal{L}[\cos at] = \frac{s}{s^2 + a^2}
\frac{d}{dt}(\cos at) = -a\sin at
\int \cos at \, dt = \frac{1}{a}\sin at
